  npcName: Bob Green
  npcPortrait: {fileID: -4431272134881128097, guid: 2c3dbcdb3752838418af6a92f13bed33, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Hello Fin!
  - Your father was the greatest angler I ever knew...
  - He set out on the Dogfish Run in search of the famous Rainbow Plaice and was
    never heard from or seen again.
  - Now his rod passes to you, you are the last of that bloodline, there is no other!
  - Put aside the boy. Become the Angler you were born to be.
  - Complete the Dogfish Run!
